{"tid":1957351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際線］HK CNN報導：唔使拗！香港完美示範帶口罩係有用","createTime":"2020-04-03T23:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T12:23:51.000Z","uid":324102,"like":525,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5cf46f67ec3e86ffeaa2e0a86025d5cc895270","tid":1957351,"uid":324102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T23:25:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/klustout/status/1246106235847524352?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fklustout%2Fstatus%2F1246106235847524352%3Fs%3D21&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e597eaae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fklustout%2Fstatus%2F1246106235847524352%3Fs%3D21&h=ba27827c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/klustout/status/1246106235847524352?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">HONG KONG&rsquo;S POSITIVE EXAMPLE IN GLOBAL DEBATE OVER MASK</span><br />\n<br />\nShould we all be wearing #masks? As governments in the West wrestle with guidance, many in Asia have been diligently wearing them *since January*. <br />\n<br />\nAnd there's growing evidence that MASKS WORK.<br />\n<br />\nHere's our report. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n駐香港CNN 女主播Kristie 做左個專題<br />\n香港完美示範帶口罩係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地經歷過SARS，有令香港人痛心既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔信個垃圾政府，自發全民帶口罩！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完全大巴大巴打落林鄭塊面<br />\n當初仲話唔需要帶口罩，帶左都要除落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴筋！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人要持堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n要繼續帶口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勤洗手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今個月情況愈來愈嚴峻，要愛惜醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要多留在家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得去retwitter &amp; say Thank you!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10bf91869e0dea898d806836e9eac1b3996dcf3","tid":1957351,"uid":190332,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"大家上twitter rt爆佢"},{"pid":"3e778d7a4e2a1fe48ec03a24e353e44adf108d2a","tid":1957351,"uid":324102,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T23:29:13.000Z","msg":"自膠 ： 係Retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551c154a0c22c4ad15d7546a78e720ab8a73f186","tid":1957351,"uid":324102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T23:43:48.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8935ecbea103e9bac68893fdea25f2b45e15a1c1","tid":1957351,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T23:59:22.000Z","msg":"原來真係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢隊人係青衣公園，但佢戴住口罩怕認錯人"},{"pid":"8ba24bd5e2fcc0c36116d3631cc38131737694de","tid":1957351,"uid":324102,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T00:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tx0OBvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftx0OBvr.png&h=9d0d0f73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c321ba1f2c30a8e17bd6e8b85dc11875de3d10","tid":1957351,"